longBusinessSummary: Green Hygienics Holdings, Inc., a development stage company, intends to cultivate and process industrial hemp for extracting cannabidiol. The company was formerly known as Takedown Entertainment Inc. and changed its name to Green Hygienics Holdings Inc. in July 2012. Green Hygienics Holdings Inc. was founded in 2008 and is based in Poway, California.
